CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 18, 1945, p. 3, reads: "Wins Post - Dr. Roy T. Anderson, prominent Pittsburgh dentist, has been appointed as substitute dentist in the public schools, effective on Aug. 30.  Dr. Anderson's office is located at 1408 Wylie Avenue."
TitMainTitle: Dr. Roy T. Anderson holding teeth model in his dentist office, 1408 Wylie Avenue, Hill District
